---
// src/components/Banner.astro
---
<section class="banner">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content">
      <h1>Automatizá tus mensajes y <span>vendé más</span></h1>
      <p>
        MM SmartInbox centraliza tus conversaciones de WhatsApp, Instagram y Facebook con IA para clasificar prospectos y cerrar ventas mientras dormís.
      </p>
      <div class="buttons">
        <a href="#prueba" class="btn btn-primary">Empezar Prueba Gratuita</a>
        <a href="#demo" class="btn btn-secondary">Ver Demo</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="graphic">
      <div class="dashboard-mockup">
        <div class="mockup-header">
          <div class="icon-bot">
             <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" width="24" height="24">
               <path d="M12 2C8.13 2 5 5.13 5 9C5 10.42 5.43 11.73 6.16 12.84C5.9 14.38 5 16 5 16C5 16 7.5 15.65 9.17 14.73C10.05 14.9 11 15 12 15C15.87 15 19 11.87 19 8C19 4.13 15.87 2 12 2Z" fill="white"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="bot-info">
             <strong>Nova</strong>
             <span class="status">EN LÍNEA</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mockup-chat">
          <div class="msg bubble-user">¡Hola! Estoy interesado en el plan Pro. ¿Qué incluye?</div>
          <div class="msg bubble-bot">
             <div class="check-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z" fill="var(--color-primary-green)"/></svg>
             </div>
             ¡Hola! El plan Pro incluye IA avanzada, integraciones ilimitadas y soporte 24/7. ¿Te gustaría agendar una demo?
          </div>
          <div class="tag-badge">Prospecto Caliente</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="laptop-overlay">
         <img src="/images/Banner.png" alt="Dashboard" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .banner {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    min-height: calc(100vh - 84px);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    background: #eeeeeeff;
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    width: 90%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4rem;
  }
  .content {
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 550px;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 3.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.15;
    color: #1a1a2e;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    letter-spacing: -1.5px;
  }
  h1 span {
    color: var(--color-primary-blue);
  }
  p {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text-medium);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .btn {
    padding: 0.8rem 1.8rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    background-color: var(--color-primary-green);
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(21, 198, 59, 0.2);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background-color: #12ad33;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .btn-secondary {
    background-color: #f6f7ff;
    color: var(--color-primary-blue);
    border: 1px solid #dbeafe;
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-primary-blue);
    background-color: #ecf3ff;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  
  /* Right side graphic */
  .graphic {
    flex: 1;
    position: relative;
    height: 400px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-end;
  }
  .dashboard-mockup {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 480px;
    width: 100%;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    border: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }
  .mockup-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .icon-bot {
    background: var(--color-primary-blue);
    color: white;
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .bot-info strong {
    display: block;
    color: var(--color-text-dark);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .bot-info .status {
    color: var(--color-primary-green);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .mockup-chat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }
  .msg {
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 85%;
    position: relative;
  }
  .bubble-user {
    background: #eef2f6;
    color: #334155;
    border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }
  .bubble-bot {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    color: #475569;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }
  .check-icon {
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    left: 20px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .tag-badge {
    align-self: flex-start;
    background: #e6f9ec;
    color: var(--color-primary-green);
    padding: 0.35rem 0.85rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .laptop-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -50px;
    left: -20px;
    width: 260px;
    height: 200px;
    z-index: 2;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    border: 6px solid #111;
    background: #111;
  }
  
  .laptop-overlay img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .container {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
    .buttons {
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .graphic {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .laptop-overlay {
       display: none;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .banner {
      padding: 4rem 0;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .btn {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .dashboard-mockup {
      padding: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .msg {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
